ent-AU14DesertM10CorpsmanHelmet = Desert M10 Corpsman Helmet
    .desc = Standard Issue Helmet used by USCM. Provides modest protection from bullet and melee attacks at the head. It also has an inbuilt camera allowing for command staff to observe the squad's actions. This one is painted with the red cross.
ent-AU14DesertM10Helmet = Desert M10 Helmet
